title: Bobby Makes A Big Change To His Will + Amy's Daughter Has Been Doing Something Unsafe + Ansley Watson From KATV-TV Fills In For Lunchbox
itunes:title: Bobby Makes A Big Change To His Will + Amy's Daughter Has Been Doing Something Unsafe + Ansley Watson From KATV-TV Fills In For Lunchbox
description:
Bobby revisited his will yesterday and made a very big change. Amy's daughter learned something from television that freaked Amy out. She had to have a talk with her daughter about safety. Plus, Bobby's friend Ansley Watson from KATV-TV in Little Rock, Arkansas joined us in studio to fill in for Lunchbox!
